## 10. Explicit DO NOT
- Do not build the exploration loop, frontier, AppMap, auth, or framework detection.
- Do not call any language model.
- Do not containerize.
- Do not have `observe()` click, type, or navigate — it only reads.
- Do not include any real URL, field name, or data value in any log, test, or report.
